Wani masanin jami'ar Michigan, Tiffany Ng, ya kuma lura cewa wannan shi ne ƙaho na farko a duniya da aka yi magana da shi ta hanyar Dionisio A. Lind, wani ɗan baƙar fata, wanda ya yi wani babban ƙaho a cocin Riverside shekaru 18 da suka wuce.
Merriweather ya ce St. Martin ba ta ba da wani aiki a matsayinta ba.
A cikin 'yan watannin da suka gabata, an sami matsala a St. Martin's, inda gine-gine da kuma masu sana'a suka shiga, wanda aka haɗa da shugabancin coci na duniya da kuma bishop's office.
