Scott Robinson ya yi nasara wajen kare abokin hamayyarsa amma ya yi tsalle sosai, sai Alan Lithgow ya yi ƙoƙari sosai bayan ya yi tsalle don ya kai ga Craig Halkett a gaban ƙwallon ƙafa.
