Shugaban kasar Mexico ya yi alkawarin cewa ba zai tura sojojinsa zuwa yaki da fararen hula ba
A ranar tunawa da shekara ta 50 da zanga-zangar da dalibai ke yi a Mexico, shugaban kasar Andrés Manuel López Obrador ya yi alkawarin cewa ba zai taba amfani da sojojinsa a kan fararen hula ba.
López Obrador a filin Tlatelolco a ranar Asabar ya yi alkawarin cewa ba zai taba amfani da sojojinsa ba don ya danne al'ummar Mexico.
A ranar 2 ga Oktoba, 1968, sojojin soja sun yi wa masu zanga-zangar lumana wuta a filin, inda suka kashe mutane 300 a lokacin da ƙungiyoyin ɗaliban hagu suka nuna alamun karuwa a Latin Amurka.
López Obrador ya yi alkawarin cewa zai taimaka wa matasa a Mexico ta hanyar ba da tallafin kuɗi na wata-wata ga ɗalibai, kuma yana shirin kafa ƙarin jami'o'i na gwamnati kyauta.
Ya ce rashin aikin yi da rashin ilimi sune manyan abubuwan da ke sa matasa su shiga hannun ƙungiyoyin laifi.
Ya kamata Amurka ta ninka tsarin samar da kudi don magance matsalar I.I.
Yayin da kasar Sin ta ƙara kasancewa da himma wajen bincike da ci gaban fasaha ta wucin gadi, Amurka ta bukaci ta ninka tallafin da ake ba da ga wannan bincike, in ji Kai-Fu Lee, mai saka jari da kuma mai amfani da hanyoyin amfani da fasaha ta wucin gadi, wanda ya yi aiki a Google da Microsoft da kuma Apple.
Ya ce gwamnatin Amirka ta yi sanarwa game da ayyukan fasaha na wucin gadi, duk da cewa ba ta da wata manufa ta musamman ta yin amfani da su.
A lokacin, kasar Sin ta sanar da shirin da ta yi na zama babbar mai bunkasa fasaha ta duniya a shekarar 2030.
"Ƙara sau biyu a cikin kuɗin bincike na I.M. zai zama farkon farawa, tun da yake dukan sauran ƙasashe suna da ƙarancin matsayi a kan Amurka, kuma za a yi wani sabon ci gaba a fannin I.M"., in ji Lee.
Ta hanyar ninka tallafin bincike, zai iya ninka yiwuwar Amurka ta yi babban mataki na gaba a fannin ilimin kere kere, in ji ta a wata hira da CNBC.
Lee, wanda ya wallafa littafinsa mai suna AI Superpowers: China, Silicon Valley and the New World Order, ya fito ne a wannan watan a karkashin jagorancin Houghton Mifflin Harcourt, babban jami'in Sinovation Ventures, wanda ya yi wani zuba jari a Face++, daya daga cikin manyan kamfanonin fasaha a kasar Sin.
A shekarun 1980, ya yi aiki a Jami'ar Carnegie Mellon a kan tsarin AI wanda ya ci nasara a kan mafi kyawun ɗan wasan kwaikwayo na Amurka na Othello, kuma daga baya ya zama memba na gudanarwa na Microsoft Research, da kuma shugaban sashen Google na kasar Sin.
Lee ya amince da nasarar da gwamnatin Amirka ta bayar game da gasa ta fasaha, ciki har da DARPA Robotics Challenge, kuma ya yi mamakin lokacin da za ta shirya irin wannan taron na gaba domin zai ba da damar gano sababbin masu tsarawa a nan gaba.
Lee ya ce, masu bincike a Amirka suna aiki tuƙuru don samun tallafin gwamnati don bincike.
Ba kasar Sin ce ke cin gajiyar manyan masana kimiyya ba, manyan kamfanoni ne ke cin gajiyar su.
Facebook da Google da sauran kamfanonin fasaha sun yi amfani da su a shekarun baya don su yi aiki a fannin I.M.
Lee ya ce, sauya manufofin shige da fice na iya taimakawa wajen bunkasa kokarin da Amurka ke yi na yin amfani da fasahar kere kere.
"Ina ganin ya kamata a ba da takardar kore ta atomatik ga waɗanda suke da digiri na biyu a fannin ilimin kere kere", in ji shi.
A watan Yuli na 2017, Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ta sanar da shirin bunkasa ilimin kere kere na zamani na gaba.
A cewar Lee, a kasar Sin, National Science Foundation na kasar Sin na tallafawa ma'aikatan cibiyoyin ilimi kamar yadda National Science Foundation da sauran kungiyoyin gwamnati ke ba da kudi ga masu bincike a Amurka, amma a kasar Sin, aikin ilimi ya fi muni.
A wannan shekara, Ma'aikatar Tsaro ta kafa Cibiyar Artificial Intelligence ta Ƙungiyar AI, inda masana'antu da masana kimiyya za su iya aiki tare, kuma Fadar White House ta sanar da kafa wata kwamiti mai suna Select Committee on Artificial Intelligence.
A wannan watan, DARPA ta zuba jari dala biliyan biyu a wani shiri mai suna AI Next,
kuma a halin yanzu, NSF tana kashe dala miliyan 100 a shekara don tallafawa bincike na AI.
A lokacin, dokokin Amirka da ke shirin kafa Kwamitin I.A. na Tsaro na Kasa sun yi watanni ba su yi wani aiki ba.
A Makidoniya, ana gudanar da kuri'un raba gardama kan sauya sunan ƙasar
A zaben da aka yi a ranar Lahadi, 'yan Macedonia sun amince da sauya sunan ƙasar zuwa Jamhuriyar Macedonia ta Arewa, don warware rashin jituwa da ta yi shekaru da yawa da ta hana ƙasar shiga cikin EU da NATO.
Girka, wadda ake kira Macedonia a cikin lardinta, ta yi jayayya cewa sunan makwabciyarta ta arewa yana nuna cewa tana neman yankin Girka mai suna iri ɗaya, saboda haka ta yi amfani da veto a kan kasancewa mamba a NATO da EU.
A watan Yuni, gwamnatocin biyu sun cimma yarjejeniya game da sabon sunan jihar, amma masu adawa da motsin zuciyar kasa sun ce sauya sunan zai lalata asalin kabilar Macedonia, wanda yawancin Slavic ne.
Shugaban kasa Gjorge Ivanov ya bayyana cewa ba zai halarci zaben ba, kuma sakamakon yakin neman zaben da aka kaddamar ya haifar da shakku game da samun kashi 50% na masu halartar zaben da ake bukata.
Tambayar da aka yi a kan takardun zabe ita ce: Shin kuna goyon bayan kasancewar NATO da EU na ƙasarku kuma kuna amincewa da yarjejeniyar da kuka yi da Girka?
Masu goyon bayan sauya sunan, da Firayim Minista Zoran Zaev a gaba, sun yi jayayya cewa wannan farashin ya cancanci biya domin Macedonia, a matsayin daya daga cikin ƙasashen da suka tashi daga cikin rushewar Yugoslavia, ta sami damar shiga EU da NATO.
'Na zo ne a yau don in yi zabe a kan makomar kasar domin matasan Makidoniya su rayu cikin 'yanci a ƙarƙashin kariya ta Tarayyar Turai domin hakan zai sa mu kasance da kwanciyar hankali,' Olivera Georgijevska (79) ta ce a Skopje.
Ko da yake kuri'un ba su da tilastawa ta doka, wani dan majalisa mai yawa ya bayyana cewa yana jin wajibi ne a kan sakamakon kuri'un.
Don canja sunan, ana bukatar rinjaye na kashi biyu bisa uku a majalisar.
Hukumar zabe ta jihar ta ce ba a samu wani rahoto game da rashin daidaito ba har zuwa karfe 13:00 na ranar zabe.
Amma, har zuwa yanzu, yawan masu jefa kuri'a ya kai kashi 16 cikin dari, wanda ya kai kashi 34 cikin dari a zaben majalisar dokokin kasar na 2016 (wanda ya kai kashi 66 cikin dari na masu jefa kuri'a da suka yi rajista).
'Na zo ne domin in yi zabe domin 'ya'yana domin mu ne muke bukatar mu zauna a Turai,' in ji Gjose Tanevski (62) wanda ya kada kuri'arsa a Skopje, babban birnin kasar.
