Turai za ta iya fara wasan karshe na gasar Ryder Cup da kyau bayan ta kammala wasan hudu da hudu da aka buga a ranar Asabar da ta yi wa Amurka nasara da kashi 10 zuwa 6.
Tommy Fleetwood da Francesco Molinari sun yi nasara a wasan, sun ci Tiger Woods da ke ci gaba da raunana, kuma sun ci gaba da samun maki hudu a filin wasa na Le Golf National.
