Akwai wasu lokatai masu kyau a fim din Johnny English na baya-bayan nan.
Na yi farin ciki da yadda Johnny English ya yi tafiya a cikin makamai na tsakiya zuwa wani jirgi mai saukar ungulu, kuma bayan ya kai can, sai rotors suka yi ta ta ta da shi a kan kwalkwali na 'yan mintoci kaɗan.
Atkinson yana da halayyar ban dariya a fim, amma ba shi da ban dariya, kuma yana da ban dariya, saboda a yau, manyan fina-finai kamar James Bond da kuma Mission Impossible suna amfani da abin dariya.
Ina jin cewa fim din yana da ban dariya ga yara, kuma a ganina, Johnny English ya yi nasara a kan abubuwan da ya yi da ba su dace ba, ba su kai matakin da Atkinson ya nuna na basira da basira a cikin jerin Mr. Bean ba.
A cikin fim din, an soma da cewa, "Ingilishi tana cikin haɗari mai tsanani".
Wani dan aikata laifuka na yanar gizo ya shiga cikin hanyar sadarwar yanar gizo mai zurfi ta hanyar leken asiri ta Burtaniya, kuma ya bayyana asalin dukkan jami'an Burtaniya ga babban firgita na jami'in harkokin kasuwanci Kevin Eldon, wanda abin takaici, ya samu karamin rawar da aka yi a fim din.
