Ministan Cikin Gida: Amurka za ta yi amfani da takunkumin hana fitar da makamashi daga Rasha
Idan ya cancanta, Washington zai yi amfani da rundunar soji don hana jigilar kayayyakin samar da makamashi na Rasha zuwa kasuwa, don haka ba za a iya samun makamashin Rasha zuwa gabas ta tsakiya ba, in ji Ministan Harkokin Cikin Gida na Amurka Ryan Zinke a Washington Examiner.
Zinke ya ce kasancewar Rasha a Syria  musamman ma game da ayyukan da Rasha ta yi a kan bukatar gwamnatin Syria mai kyau  wani dalili ne kawai na samun sabbin kasuwannin makamashi.
"Ina ganin suna cikin yankin gabas ta tsakiya ne kawai domin suna son sayar da makamashi a can, kamar yadda suke yi a gabashin Turai da kudancin Turai", Zinke ya ce a wata sanarwa.
Ministan harkokin cikin gida ya ce akwai hanyoyin da za a hana Rashawa yin hakan.
"Amurka tana da karfin ta wajen samar da jiragen ruwa da ke buɗewa, kuma tana iya toshe hanyoyin ta a lokacin da ta bukaci hakan, don ta tabbata cewa ba a samu wutar lantarki daga Rasha a kasuwa ba", in ji Zinke.
Zinke ya yi magana ne ga masu halartar taron da kungiyar mai zaman kanta ta Consumer Energy Alliance ta shirya.
A jawabinsa, ya kwatanta yadda Washington ke yin amfani da shi wajen yaƙi da Rasha da Iran, kuma ya lura cewa waɗannan hanyoyin suna da yawa.
A cewar Zinke, za a iya yin amfani da irin wannan matakin na cin hanci da rashawa a kan Iran da Rasha, ta hanyar amfani da masu amfani da makamashi da ke akwai da kuma gabatar da sababbin makamashi, inda ya kira Rasha tattalin arziki mai girma, yana nuna dogaro da kasar kan masu amfani da makamashi.
Sanarwar ta yi daidai da shirin gwamnatin Trump na fitar da gas mai guba zuwa Turai, yana tura Rasha daga kasuwa wanda ke ba da zaɓi mafi arha ga masu amfani da Turai.
Saboda haka manyan jami'an gwamnatin Trump, ciki har da shugaban, sun rinjayi Jamus ta janye daga aikin da ake kira Northern Stream 2, wanda idan ya faru zai sa Jamus ta zama ruwan Moscow.
A wani lokaci, Moscow ta nuna cewa, da ake bukatar karin karfin da ake da shi, da kuma karin karfin da ake da shi zuwa mita 110,000,000,000, da kuma da ake bukatar karin dala biliyan 11 na North Stream 2, aikin tattalin arziki ne kawai.
A cewar Kremlin, Washington ta yi tsayayya da wannan aikin da gaggawa saboda dalilai na tattalin arziki, wanda ya nuna rashin adalci.
Ina tsammanin muna da ra'ayi ɗaya game da kada a yi amfani da makamashi don yin amfani da shi a cikin matsi, kuma dole ne a ba masu amfani da damar zaɓar masu samar da su kyauta  Ministan Makamashi na Rasha Aleksandr Novak ya bayyana bayan ganawa da Ministan Makamashi na Amurka Rick Perry a Moscow a watan Satumba.
