An tsare matar a Texas.
Masu gabatar da kara na jihohin da ke goyon bayan Grace sun bayyana El Salvador da Honduras da kuma Guatemala a matsayin wuraren da ake neman mafaka a Amurka domin suna da matsala ta rikicin gida da kuma gangami a waɗannan ƙasashe.
Sabon manufar 'yan gudun hijira ta Amurka ta janye wani hukunci na 2014 da Hukumar Daukaka kara ta 'Yan Shige da Fice ta (BIA) ta yanke, wanda ya ba da damar yin neman mafaka ga baƙi marasa takaddun ba, suna gudun hijira daga tashin hankali a cikin iyali.
A wata sanarwa da aka fitar a ranar Juma'a, Babban Shari'a na Washington, D.C., Karl Racine ya ce sabuwar manufar ta yi watsi da dokokin jihar, tarayya da na duniya da suka shafe shekaru da yawa.
A karkashin dokar tarayya, duk bukatar mafaka dole ne a yi la'akari da gaskiyar da ke akwai a kowane hali, kuma irin wannan cikas ya saɓa wa wannan ka'ida  a cikin wasiƙar da aka rubuta ta hanyar masana.
Masu gabatar da kara sun kuma bayyana a cikin wasiƙar cewa, manufar hana shige da fice na ba da dama ga tattalin arzikin Amurka, domin shige da fice na shige da fice na zama 'yan kasuwa da kuma cika mafi ƙasƙanci na jobs.
A watan Yuni, babban lauya Jeff Sessions ya umurci alƙalan da ke kula da mafaka kada su ba da mafaka ga waɗanda suka yi fama da tashin hankali a gida da kuma 'yan bindiga.
