A shekara ta 1994, Berners-Lee ya canja Intanet ta wajen kafa Ƙungiyar Yanar Gizo ta Duniya a Jami'ar Fasaha ta Massachusetts.
Berners-Lee ya kasance babban mai ba da shawara a cikin 'yan watannin nan a cikin muhawara game da tsaka tsaki na Intanet.
Duk da cewa Berners-Lee ya kaddamar da Inrupt, ya ci gaba da kasancewa mai kafa da kuma darektan World Wide Web Consortium, Web Foundation, da Open Data Institute.
"Ina da kyakkyawan fata game da zamanin da za a yi amfani da intanet", in ji Berners-Lee.
