Dan Danish din ya fara fitowa a wasan Walderram na 1997, inda kungiyar da Seve Ballesteros ta jagoranci ta samu nasara ta biyar a kan Amurkawa, sannan a karshe suka samu nasarar ci gaba da samun nasara ta gashin gashi guda daya.
"Ya kamata mu tuna wa kanmu cewa ko da yake mun samu nasara a Valderrama, amma mun ci nasara ne da gashin gashi guda ɗaya, kuma mun samu nasara a Brookline, inda muka yi nasara", in ji Bjørn a hoton nan bayan nasarar da ya samu a aji na 2018 na 5'3 a ranar Juma'a da kuma jiya, wanda ya kai su 10'6 a filin wasa na Le Golf National.
 Idan muka yi tunani game da wasannin da aka yi a shekarun baya, za mu ga cewa wasan bai ƙare ba tukuna.
Za ku yi wasa da ƙarfi sosai gobe.
Don haka, mu tafi mu yi duk abin da ya kamata mu yi don mu yi nasara.
Ba za mu iya shakatawa ba har sai an rubuta maki a kan allon.
Muna da burin da muke so mu samu wannan kyautar kuma wannan shi ne abin da muke bukatar mu mai da hankali ga shi.
Kamar yadda na fada a baya, na fi sha'awar 'yan wasanmu 12, amma dole ne mu kula da sauran 'yan wasan da suka fi girma a duniya.
Bjørn, mai alfahari da aikin da ƙungiyar ta yi a kan tseren da ya yi wuya, ya ce: "Ba zan taɓa yin annabci ba a irin wannan yanayin.
Ranar gobe ta zama ta daban.
Hakan zai iya faruwa ne idan mutum ya yi nasara, kuma hakan ya bambanta da wasan da ake yi a rukuni.
Yana da kyau a yi wasa a cikin ma'aurata idan abubuwa suna tafiya daidai, amma idan mutum ya fita dabam, zai bayyana a kowane fannin abin da ɗan wasan golf yake.
Dole ne a sanar da 'yan wasan wannan don su fito da mafi kyawun su a filin wasa gobe.
Za su rabu da abokansu, kuma za su kasance da kyau.
Ba kamar Bjørn ba, Jim Furyk, wanda ya jagoranci tawagar da ke gaba da shi, ya amince da cewa 'yan wasansa za su yi nasara a wasan da ke gaba da su fiye da na biyu, sai dai Jordan Spieth da Justin Thomas, waɗanda suka ci maki uku daga cikin hudu.
Furyk ya shaida bangarorin biyu na tashin matattu na ranar ƙarshe: a Brookline, ya kasance memba na ƙungiyar da ta ci nasara, sannan ya kasance a kan ɓangaren da ta rasa bayan da ƙungiyar Turai ta yi nasara a matsayin abin al'ajabi a Medinah.
"Na tuna da dukan kalmomin da aka yi masa" "ya amsa lokacin da aka tambaye shi, domin ya ƙarfafa 'yan wasan kafin ranar ƙarshe ta hannun Ben Crenshaw a shekara ta 1999.
Muna da manyan wasanni 12 a gobe, amma muna da gaggawa a farkon, kamar yadda muka gani a Brooklyn, kamar yadda muka gani a Medinah.
Idan wani rukuni ya yi nasara, zai sa 'yan wasan su yi wasa a tsakiya.
Mun shirya jerin abubuwan da za su faru kuma mun shirya 'yan wasanmu su yi mu'ujiza na gaske a gobe.
An ba Thomas aiki na jagorantar ƙoƙarin juyawa, kuma zai buga wasan Rory McIlroy a wasan farko, sannan Paul Casey, Justin Rose, Jon Rahm, Tommy Fleetwood da Ian Poulter a jere, a matsayin farkon rabin ƙungiyar Turai.
