Girgizar Kasa da Ruwan Sama a Indonesia
Akalla mutane 384 ne suka mutu a lokacin da wata girgizar ƙasa mai karfin gaske ta afku a birnin Palu, Indonesia, a ranar Jumma'a.
Har ila yau, an lalata hanyar sadarwa a yankin, saboda haka har yanzu babu wani labari daga gwamnatin Donggala da ke arewacin Palut, inda girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfi 7.5 ta kasance.
An yi wa mazauna garin da ke cikin garin da ke da mazauna fiye da 16,000 aikin kwashe su.
Wasu bayanai masu muhimmanci game da Palur da Donggala a tsibirin Celebes:
Palu, babban birnin yankin Celebes ta Tsakiya, an gina shi a yammacin tsibirin Celebes, a ƙarshen wani kusurwar bakin teku, a cikin 2017 an kiyasta yawan mutane 379,800.
A lokacin da aka yi bikin cika shekara 40 da aka kafa birnin, girgizar ƙasa da ruwan sama sun afku a birnin.
Gwamnatin Donggala tana da nisan mil 300 a arewa maso yammacin tsibirin Celebes.
A shekara ta 2017, yawan mutanen da ke cikin ƙananan hukumomi fiye da lardin  sun kai kimanin 299,200.
Tsakiyar Tsakiya tana da al'ada ta kifi da gona, musamman a yankin Donggala na bakin teku.
Masana'antar nickel tana da muhimmanci a harkar tattalin arziki, amma tana da yawa a Morowali, a gabashin tekun Celebes.
Hukumar kula da bala'i ta Indonesia ta ce, a cikin shekaru 100 da suka shige, an yi ruwan sama a birnin Palut da Donggala sau da yawa.
A shekara ta 1938, wata ruwan sama mai rufi ya halaka mazauna birnin kuma ya halaka ɗaruruwan gidaje a birnin Donggala.
A shekara ta 1996, wata babbar rigakafi ta afku a yankin Yammacin Donga, kuma mutane tara sun mutu.
Indonesia tana cikin yankin da ake kira Pacific Ring of Fire, kuma hakan ya sa girgizar ƙasa take faruwa a kai a kai.
Wasu daga cikin manyan girgizar ƙasa da kuma tsananin tashin hankali da aka yi a shekarun baya:
2004: Ranar 26 ga watan Disamba, wata babbar girgizar ruwa ta afku a gabar yammacin lardin Aceh a Arewacin Sumatra, ta jawo wata girgizar ruwa mai zurfi da ta kai kasashe 14, ta kashe mutane 226,000 a gabar tekun Tekun Indiya, fiye da rabin wadanda suka mutu a Aceh.
2005: Girgizar ƙasa mai tsanani ta girgiza yammacin Sumatra tsakanin ƙarshen Maris da farkon Afrilu.
A tsibirin Nias, kusa da Sumatra, an kashe ɗaruruwan mutane.
2006: Girgizar ƙasa mai karfin awo 6.8 ta girgiza yankin kudu na tsibirin Java, mafi yawan jama'a a Indonesia, kuma ta jawo raƙuman ruwa kusan 700 a bakin tekun kudu.
2009: Girgizar ƙasa mai karfin 7.6 ta yi barna a kusa da Padang, babban birnin lardin West Sumatra.
Mutane fiye da 1,100 ne suka rasa rayukansu.
2010: Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin 7.5 ta girgiza tsibirin Mentawai kusa da Sumatra, kuma ta jawo wata dutse mai tsawon mita 10 a wani wuri, wadda ta halaka ƙauyuka da yawa kuma ta kashe kusan mutane 300.
2016: Girgizar ƙasa ta afkawa gwamnatin Aceh Pidie Jaya, kuma tsoro da halaka da ta biyo baya ya sa mutane da yawa su tuna da mummunan farashin da aka yi a 2004.
Ba a yi ruwan sama a wannan lokacin ba, amma har ila yau, ya kashe fiye da mutane 100 a ƙarƙashin gine-ginen da suka rushe.
2018: Lombok tsibiri ne mai yawan yawon bude ido a Indonesia; girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfi ta kashe mutane 500 a nan, musamman a arewacin tsibirin.
Dubban gine-gine sun zama ƙasa, kuma dubban masu yawon buɗe ido sun makale a tsibirin a wani lokaci.
