An bayyana cewa, 'Yan uwan Diego Enrique Angelini, Nicholas Cleves, Ann-Laure Decadt, Darren Drake, Ariel Erlij, Hernan Ferruchi, Hernan Diego Mendoza da Alejandro Damian Pagnucco sun yi wa Saipov azaba da rashi.
Wadanda aka kashe su biyar 'yan yawon bude ido ne daga Argentina.
A cikin shekaru goma da suka shige, gundumar New York ta Kudu ta bukaci a yanke hukuncin kisa a kan wanda ake zargi.
An yanke wa Khalid Barnes hukuncin kisa a kan wasu 'yan kasuwa biyu, amma a watan Satumbar shekara ta 2009, an yanke masa hukuncin daurin rai a kurkuku.
A wani shari'a ta tarayya a birnin New York, an yanke wa mutanen hukuncin kisa a shekara ta 1953, kuma a wani shari'a kuma, an yanke wa Julius da Ethel Rosenberg hukuncin kisa shekaru biyu kafin a yi musu wannan shari'ar don yin leƙen asiri ga Soviet Union a lokacin Yaƙin Tsakiya.
An kashe Rosenberg biyu a kan kujera mai lantarki a ranar 19 ga Yuni, 1953.
A cikin takardun kotu, an rubuta cewa Saipov, wanda aka haifa a Uzbekistan, bai nuna cewa ya yi nadama ba a cikin kwanaki da watanni da suka biyo bayan harin.
A lokacin da aka yi masa tambayoyi, ya ce yana farin cikin yin hakan.
